name: DragonMoon
description: DragonMoon, or DMoon is based on the dragons of Chinese mythology, legendary beasts that are masters of transformation and all things. Through thousands of years of cultivation and heritage within Chinese culture, dragons have come to symbolize the Chinese people. DMoon aims to proliferate the dragon’s spirit of improvement, boundless energy, and indomitable will to express the exaltation of Chinese culture and bring the world’s crypto investors together.
